333
00:17:02,670 --> 00:17:03,350
So?

334
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:06,160
It's quite complicated

335
00:17:07,040 --> 00:17:08,040
and we'd better stay covert

336
00:17:08,040 --> 00:17:09,590
on the way.

337
00:17:09,680 --> 00:17:10,590
Don't let anyone know

338
