531
00:27:20,800 --> 00:27:21,560
So,

532
00:27:21,800 --> 00:27:23,400
we'll have to wait

533
00:27:23,680 --> 00:27:24,350
for other chances

534
00:27:24,400 --> 00:27:26,230
after we get back to the capital city.

535
00:27:28,590 --> 00:27:29,400
Wang Qinian!

